{
  "texts": [
    "To figure out the severity of this, we need to distinguishing short-term from long-term aspects.",
    "In the short run, a scenario-based risk assessments may indeed deter AI deployment and investment.",
    "To mitigate this, different strategies might be recommended to make our proposal more sustainable.",
    "Firstly, European legislation might indicate, in the AIA's implementing acts, the key risk drivers for each broad AI scopes already outlined in the regulation (e.g., in the Annex III).",
    "This would ease the task of deployers and minimizes arbitrariness in the AIA's enforcement."
  ]
}